{"tid":612304,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"覺唔覺去唱K，當中有毒撚就會好撚難頂？","createTime":"2018-03-31T17:46:48.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-01T09:03:24.000Z","uid":12034,"like":24,"dislike":43,"uniUserReply":30,"replies":[{"pid":"8fdcb4b4ac0128ab14f878d564038bbe189ce515","tid":612304,"uid":12034,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-31T17:46:48.000Z","msg":"1. 毒撚最鍾意一係幫你和音 一係同你伴唱<br />\n一齊唱都算啦 仲要唔係成首唱<br />\n剩係唱副歌 一句<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n都算撚數 好死唔死仲要唱改詞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n一係就乜鳩都改隻字做粗口<br />\n一係就足球歌 一係就政治歌<br />\n同時佢就會點一大堆歌，話幫你地點，一齊唱之類<br />\n但自己又唔敢獨唱，一問到[呢首邊個點嫁？咁到你唱啦]<br />\n佢就會話[我睇下MV者，無人唱就飛啦]<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n2. 好似唔食哂間餐廳d野就蝕本咁<br />\nkbuf乜鳩都拎黎食 成晚唔係禁電話就食<br />\n野飲一人兩杯 根本就飲唔哂<br />\n佢就會係咁問 有野飲呀!!邊個飲呀!!唔洗錢唔好哂呀!!!<br />\n然後就爭住幫人落單<br />\n好死唔死 嗌走管<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n知有女在場就想show自己幾環保幾乜柒咁<br />\n我屌你老母咩<br />\n<br />\n同自己fd當然無呢d情況，但大班人出黎既點都會有一兩件呢d咁既人，唔熟又唔可以當面屌，搞到氣氛好撚老尷<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c60854e255048b02f36d6b3c7c82b38213547616","tid":612304,"uid":149151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-31T17:47:30.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"d7f29411214e4660c3ac76d7b9a771f08264e1cd","tid":612304,"uid":12034,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"c60854e255048b02f36d6b3c7c82b38213547616","tid":612304,"uid":149151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-31T17:47:30.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-31T17